"'''Zygerrian Takedown'''" was a free online supplement published by [[Wizards of the Coast]] on [[July 24]], [[2003]]. The mini-adventure was written by [[Jason Fry]] for the [[Star Wars Roleplaying Game]].

The mini-adventure is set in the [[Rise of the Empire era]] and is designed for four player characters in the 8&ndash;10 level range. As with almost all adventures, the time period and character levels can be adjusted as needed.

